Class Hogwarts

  • java.lang.Object
    • Hogwarts
  • public class Hogwarts
extends Object
    This class stores information about Hogwarts. It contains different collections to store Hogwart's houses, characters that are going to duel, generic wands and characters with no energy points left.
    Version:
    5/12/2019
    Author:
    Jorge Cancho Casado, Rubén Costa Barriga and Arturo Mejías Velasco

      • removeDuelingCharacters

        public String removeDuelingCharacters()
        Removes every character from the duelingCharacters collection returning them to their respective houses. If a character has no energy points left, it sends it to the dungeon. It also returns the information of what happens to every character after dueling as a String.
        Returns:
        String - The information that is going to be shown.
